title: still missing the cosmic ruins icon after the event ended.
body: Any way to get help on this?

replies.body: Don't fret just yet! Those icons are still going out until **[5/29](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/page/learn-more-about-dark-star-2017)**. If you don't have it by that date, shoot us a ticket and we can look into it.
